[site24x7_api_site24x7://<name>]
client_id = Enter the client unique ID
client_secret = Go to https://api-console.zoho.com, create a Self Client, and copy the generated Client ID and Client Secret for authentication.
authorization_code = Enter the scope "Site24x7.Reports.ALL" to allow the API to access your account details.
site24x7_account_domain = Enter your Site24x7 account domain.For example: site24x7.com, site24x7.eu, site24x7.in, site24x7.jp, etc.